reviewText: Could use a lot more substance as a documentary, had a lot of people telling how much they liked Pilates but lacking on actual information and methods.
It was informative. I could have done without the unicornesque hyper aesthetic practicing pilates by the sea shots, but that's just me.
very good documentary about pilates and how it got its start
A lot of people don't know anything about Pilates, but this was an awesome and educational video. I've since enrolled in a one-on-one class that I expect to be phenomenal.
A great documentary film about Pilates. Everyone should see this!
Get this movie if you want to know more about the essence of Pilates and it's true potential to help people
Artful representation of an incredible movement of the human race. Very inspiring!
